# Results Directory

This directory contains experiment outputs including:
- Fine-tuned model checkpoints
- Inference results and segmentation masks
- Extracted coordinates
- Evaluation metrics

Results are organized by experiment:
- `exp2_empiar10988_finetuning/` - EMPIAR-10988 fine-tuning outputs
- `exp3_umusynth_thy/` - UMU synthetic thyroglobulin fine-tuning outputs
